<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>liáo kuò de cǎo yuán 迦南1141</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 liáo kuò de cǎo yuán shàng, niú qún yáng ér pǎo. lán lán de tiān kōng xià, duǒ duǒ bái yún piāo.
 zhè lǐ de rén men a shàn liáng yòu qín láo, yīn yǒu shén de róng guāng zhào yào, shén de róng guāng zhào yào.
 yé sū shì hǎo mù rén, bǎ wǒ men xún zhǎo. cóng cǐ zài bù jī kě, xī shuǐ qīng qīng cǎo.
 tiān fù ài wǒ men, yōu chóu biàn huān xiào. huā ér kāi le mài zi shú le, cǎo yuán shàng guǒ xiāng piāo.
 tiān fù ài wǒ men, yōu chóu biàn huān xiào. huā ér kāi le mài zi shú le, cǎo yuán shàng guǒ xiāng piāo.</lyrics>
